## Content and Channel Strategy
### Driving 40% Efficiency Gains in a Fragmented Media Landscape

@notes: The diagnosis: the content supply chain is broken. The company produces 2,400 pieces of content annually but only 14% are re-used across channels. This is a $38M annual waste problem.

